      <li><strong>Utilities:</strong> €100-180/month (electricity can be high in summer)</li>
      <li><strong>Groceries:</strong> €300-450/month</li>
      <li><strong>Dining out:</strong> €150-300/month</li>
      <li><strong>Transport:</strong> €100-200/month (car rental or taxi, limited public transport)</li>
      <li><strong>Coworking:</strong> €100-200/month (optional)</li>
